CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 22, 1967, pg. 14 reads: "Wedding Supper - Honor attendant for lovely Elaine J. Drake when she married Charles F. Bowe, was her twin sister Mrs. Elois J. Diggs, (right), Clarence J. Bowe, (left) was his brother's best man. The four are shown here at the wedding supper. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of wedding party, from left: best man Clarence J. Bowe, groom Charles F. Bowe, bride Elaine J. Drake Bowe, and bride's twin sister Elois J. Diggs, seated at banquet table during reception
